<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
group [player] : add/remove [player] to current group<br>
group all      : groups everyone following you<br>
group          : display the group you are in<br>
group pets     : groups and ungroups pets<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
To add a player to your group have them follow you then group [player]. <br>
When in a group you share experience with the other members of the group. <br>
When you have the auto_assist option turned on, you will automatically<br>
assist those in your group in battle.<br>
<br>
The group pets command groups and ungroups your pets.  The message is<br>
seen only by the group leader and works from anywhere on the game.<br>
<br>
See the help file for group looter.<br>
